{"tha-ap21:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap21:0.2":"Sihasaniyavagga ","tha-ap21:0.3":"Sopakattheraapadana ","tha-ap21:1.1":"“Pabbharam sodhayantassa, ","tha-ap21:1.2":"vipine pabbatuttame; ","tha-ap21:1.3":"Siddhattho nama bhagava, ","tha-ap21:1.4":"agacchi mama santikam. ","tha-ap21:2.1":"Buddham upagatam disva, ","tha-ap21:2.2":"lokajetthassa tadino; ","tha-ap21:2.3":"Santharam pannapetvana, ","tha-ap21:2.4":"pupphasanamadasaham. ","tha-ap21:3.1":"Pupphasane nisiditva, ","tha-ap21:3.2":"siddhattho lokanayako; ","tha-ap21:3.3":"Mamanca gatimannaya, ","tha-ap21:3.4":"aniccatamudahari. ","tha-ap21:4.1":"‘Anicca vata sankhara, ","tha-ap21:4.2":"uppadavayadhammino; ","tha-ap21:4.3":"Uppajjitva nirujjhanti, ","tha-ap21:4.4":"tesam vupasamo sukho’. ","tha-ap21:5.1":"Idam vatvana sabbannu, ","tha-ap21:5.2":"lokajettho narasabho; ","tha-ap21:5.3":"Nabham abbhuggami viro, ","tha-ap21:5.4":"hamsarajava ambare. ","tha-ap21:6.1":"Sakam ditthim jahitvana, ","tha-ap21:6.2":"bhavayaniccasannaham; ","tha-ap21:6.3":"Ekaham bhavayitvana, ","tha-ap21:6.4":"tattha kalam kato aham. ","tha-ap21:7.1":"Dve sampatti anubhotva, ","tha-ap21:7.2":"sukkamulena codito; ","tha-ap21:7.3":"Pacchime bhave sampatte, ","tha-ap21:7.4":"sapakayonupagamim. ","tha-ap21:8.1":"Agara abhinikkhamma, ","tha-ap21:8.2":"pabbajim anagariyam; ","tha-ap21:8.3":"Jatiya sattavassoham, ","tha-ap21:8.4":"arahattamapapunim. ","tha-ap21:9.1":"Araddhaviriyo pahitatto, ","tha-ap21:9.2":"Silesu susamahito; ","tha-ap21:9.3":"Tosetvana mahanagam, ","tha-ap21:9.4":"Alattham upasampadam. ","tha-ap21:10.1":"Catunnavutito kappe, ","tha-ap21:10.2":"yam kammamakarim tada; ","tha-ap21:10.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap21:10.4":"pupphadanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap21:11.1":"Catunnavutito kappe, ","tha-ap21:11.2":"yam sannam bhavayim tada; ","tha-ap21:11.3":"Tam sannam bhavayantassa, ","tha-ap21:11.4":"patto me asavakkhayo. ","tha-ap21:12.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap21:12.2":"vimokkhapi ca atthime; ","tha-ap21:12.3":"Chalabhinna sacchikata, ","tha-ap21:12.4":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap21:13.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma sopako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap21:14.1":"Sopakattherassapadanam navamam. "}